import React from 'react';
import Card from '@mui/material/Card';
import CardMedia from '@mui/material/CardMedia';
import CardContent from '@mui/material/CardContent';
import Typography  from "@mui/material/Typography";
import CardActions  from "@mui/material/CardActions";
import Button  from "@mui/material/Button";


function Caard() {


    return (
        <>
            <Card variant="outlined" 
            sx={{ maxWidth: 345 }}>
            <CardMedia
        component="img"
        width="100%"
        image="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/79811787.cms"
        alt="green iguana"
      />
      <CardContent>
      <Typography sx={{ fontSize: 14 }} color="text.secondary" gutterBottom>
          Fastfood
        </Typography>
        <Typography gutterBottom variant="h5" component="div">
        Shack Full House
        </Typography>
        <Typography variant="body2" color="text.secondary">
        130g juicy beef patty topped with yellow cheddar cheese,pepperoni and caramelized onions smothered with jalapeno sauce on a bed of jalapenos and lettuce on our fresh baked bun
        </Typography>
      </CardContent>
      <CardActions >
          <Typography variant="h2" style={{textAlign:"right"}}>
        <Button  variant="contained" size="small">Add to cart</Button>
        </Typography>
       
      </CardActions>
            </Card>
        </>
    )
}

export default Caard
